const query = $('When Called By Another Workflow').first().json.query.toLowerCase();
const todos = $('Read Todos').all().map(t => t.json);
const now = new Date();
const today = now.toISOString().split('T')[0];

// Determine intent
let intent = 'list';
let taskText = '';
let priority = 'medium';

if (query.match(/^(add|create|new|todo:)/i)) {
  intent = 'add';
  taskText = query.replace(/^(add|create|new|todo:?)\s*(todo:?)?\s*/i, '').trim();
  if (query.includes('high') || query.includes('urgent') || query.includes('important')) priority = 'high';
  if (query.includes('low')) priority = 'low';
} else if (query.match(/^(done|complete|finish|mark)/i)) {
  intent = 'complete';
  taskText = query.replace(/^(done|complete|finish|mark)\s*(done|complete|as\s+done)?\s*(with|:)?\s*/i, '').trim();
} else if (query.match(/^(delete|remove)/i)) {
  intent = 'delete';
  taskText = query.replace(/^(delete|remove)\s*(todo:?)?\s*/i, '').trim();
} else if (query.match(/(pending|today|list|show|what)/i)) {
  intent = 'list';
}

// Filter today's todos
const todayTodos = todos.filter(t => t.date === today || t.status === 'pending');
const pending = todayTodos.filter(t => t.status === 'pending');
const completed = todayTodos.filter(t => t.status === 'completed' && t.date === today);

return [{
  json: {
    intent,
    taskText,
    priority,
    today,
    pending_count: pending.length,
    completed_count: completed.length,
    pending_tasks: pending,
    completed_tasks: completed,
    all_todos: todos
  }
}];

const pending = $input.first().json.pending_tasks || [];
const completed = $input.first().json.completed_tasks || [];

let msg = `📋 *Today's Tasks*\n\n`;

if (pending.length > 0) {
  msg += `*Pending (${pending.length}):*\n`;
  pending.forEach((t, i) => {
    const icon = t.priority === 'high' ? '🔴' : t.priority === 'medium' ? '🟡' : '🟢';
    msg += `${i+1}. ${icon} ${t.task}\n`;
  });
} else {
  msg += `*No pending tasks!* 🎉\n`;
}

if (completed.length > 0) {
  msg += `\n*Completed today (${completed.length}):*\n`;
  completed.forEach((t, i) => {
    msg += `  ✅ ${t.task}\n`;
  });
}

msg += `\n_Use "add todo: <task>" to add new tasks_`;

return [{ json: { response: msg } }];

