The user wants to mark a task as complete. Find the best matching task from the pending list.

User said: {{ $json.taskText }}

Pending tasks:
{{ $json.pending_tasks.map((t, i) => `${i}: ${t.task} (id: ${t.todo_id})`).join('\n') }}

Return ONLY the todo_id of the best match, nothing else.
